- Fixed grid overflow issues with `max-width`.

### [app.js](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/app.js)
- Enabled `headerSort` on all columns.
- Refactored account switcher with deduplication and "ALL" selection.
